35 the distribution previously authorized for the separate systems. boards. This formula for
36 distribution shall be subject to approval by the Commission.
37 (d) Enforcement. – Local officers hired by the local ABC board for the merged ABC
38 system board shall have the same territorial jurisdiction that officers for each of the merged
