5 "§ 18B-208. ABC Commission bonds and funds.
6 (a) Issuance of Bonds. – As a means of raising the funds needed from time to time in the
7 design, acquisition, construction, equipping, maintenance and operation of a warehouse under
8 G.S. 18B-204(a)(3), the Commission may, with the approval of the Governor, at one time or from
