30 alcoholic beverages are exclusively provided by the holder of a mobile bar
31 services permit. The holder of a mobile bar services permit may bring
32 alcoholic beverages onto the premises and serve the alcoholic beverages at an
33 event regardless of whether there is a charge or fee for guests to attend the
34 event. This permit does not allow the retail sale of individual alcoholic
35 beverages to guests at an event.
