45 "§ 18B-204. State warehouse.
46 (a) Contracting for Private Warehouse. – The Commission shall provide for the receipt,
47 storage, and distribution of spirituous liquor by one of the following methods:
48 (1) By negotiated contract with a privately owned warehouse.
49 (2) By negotiated contract with privately owned warehouses in several regions of
